text: Ani raja mhanala, tyala (yusuphala) majhyajavala ana. Jevha sandesa pohacavinara yusuphajavala pohocala tevha yusupha mhanale, apalya rajakade parata ja ani tyanna vicara ki tya striyanci khari kahani kaya ahe, jyanni apale hata kapuna ghetale hote. Tyance kapata cangalya prakare jananara majha palanakartaca ahe
